room_title: Escape room "The Cell" by Immersion in Seattle
room_description: You are investigating a string of disappearances in the area. You get a lead to a warehouse off of Hwy 99. Once you arrive, you walk in and fall through a trap door knocking you unconscious. You awaken to a monitor with an image of someone who is presumably your captor. He tells you that you must play his game to earn your freedom before time runs out or become another delicacy for him.
